::Prowl::

Prowl blinks at Iron Raptor's words, looking at her in surprise. He 
was a bit hurt that she had passed by his question like that, but she 
was busy and it wasn't really a big deal. She could find out all 
about it by reading his mind through their psychic link anyways.

-Allright,- he replies to her and walks off after her.
